    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以L0只有input，L1放assetfinder-1。但第二层有两个工具，gauplus和httprobe-1是并行关系对吧？那第三层我打算放httpx、nuclei这些，用来承接第二层的输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gauplus-1",
        "httprobe-1",
        "httpx-1",
        "nuclei-1",
        "nuclei-2"
