      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，第三层需要两个nuclei实例，一个扫httpx的结果，另一个回头去扫gauplus发现的URL。httpx专门接httprobe-1探测到的存活主机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "httpx-1",
        "nuclei-1",
        "nuclei-2",
        "httprobe-1",
        "gauplus-1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把四层结构画出来，L0到L3。input连到assetfinder-1，assetfinder-1再连到httprobe-1。httprobe-1输出给httpx-1，httpx-1再连到nuclei-1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "input",
        "assetfinder-1",
        "httprobe-1",
        "httpx-1",
        "nuclei-1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，nuclei-1和gauplus之间也有关系。nuclei-1扫完之后，有些结果需要gauplus再去补充爬取，然后gauplus的输出给nuclei-2做二次扫描。",
      "elements_involved": [
