      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，那我调整一下连线。之前我漏了nuclei-1到gauplus-1这条线，还有gauplus-1到nuclei-2的流向。现在补上：nuclei-1指向gauplus-1，gauplus-1再指向nuclei-2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "nuclei-1",
