    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样对了，整个流程是：input → assetfinder-1 → httprobe-1 → httpx-1 → nuclei-1 → gauplus-1 → nuclei-2。gauplus-1和httprobe-1同在L2层，但数据来源不同。",
